  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop the <strong>potatoes </strong>in half lengthways then slice them into half moons</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped potatoes</strong> to a baking tray with the <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until tender but not crispy</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1627376458861-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1627376458861-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1627376458861-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1627376458861-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1627376458861-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>WARNING: </strong>The next step is a little tricky and could be dangerous so please read carefully!</p><p>Stand the <strong>sweetcorn cobettes </strong>upright on the larger flat end</p><p>Using your weight, and with your fingers well clear, push down on the knife and slice the cobettes in half lengthways</p><p>Tip: Make sure your knife is sharp. When slicing, hold the knife firmly and keep both hands above the blade. If you’re worried about slipping, chop the corn into two shorter cobs before slicing in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1627376470395-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1627376470395-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1627376470395-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1627376470395-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1627376470395-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>One by one, put the <strong>halved cobettes</strong> flat-side down</p><p>As with before, use your weight again with your fingers well clear and push down on your knife to chop them in half again, lengthways – these are your <strong>corn riblets</strong></p><p>Tip: If any naturally break apart, don't worry. They'll taste just as good!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1627376480643-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1627376480643-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1627376480643-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1627376480643-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1627376480643-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> corn riblets</strong> to a separate baking tray with the<strong> ground coriander</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the riblets are nicely coated in the spices</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until lightly golden and starting to curl slightly</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1627376487027-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1627376487027-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1627376487027-x700.jpg",
