          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1627376487027-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1627376487027-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While everything's cooking, chop the <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>into quarters</p><p>Chop the<strong> coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>coriander </strong>to a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> tomato salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1627376492460-x200.jpg",
